@Comment:	Time is 5:00
@Comment:	Dear mom , I love you. I love you all in my heart. I love my nana and papa they are nice to me. I love my cousins joe and tony. I go to church on Sunday. I go to C.C.d.
@Comment:	not really a letter although it is addressed to dear mom; It is more of a list of who she loves and what she does. Chi comes up with the content and writes letter quietly. Mot explains to EXPs that she is letting Chi write the letter without too many corrections which has been suggested by Chi's teacher; Mot helps with spacing of words , punctuation and spelling when Chi asks for help
